subtitle: the Grays known for their iconic gray or
sometimes brown skin color and slender
elongated heads are a group of Clone
slaves created by the Chaka Empire
through genetic breeding
programs they primarily belong to the
Reptoid category though smaller
populations exist with insectoid soran
amphibian or vegetal DNA physically they
have humanoid forms with long limbs
large black eyes small noses thin mouths
and often seal their vertically slit
reptilian eyes behind biometric dark
lenses they can be categorized into
small drones or Lackey and the more
powerful and intelligent tall Grays most
Grays are emotionless biosynthetic
entities integrated into human
environments on conquered planets their
motives vary widely with some involved
in abductions and experimentation While
others like the cipy are peaceful
